title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 2 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 2 2022
description:
Tucker Carlson and Chris Rufo triumph over vicious attacks and lies. Dems use fertilizer crisis as an opportunity to do more harm. Discovery+ debuts teenage drag show. The Democrat Party is now deeply immoral on gender identity issues for children. Pelosi takes virtue-signaling trip to Ukraine, tells Zelensky we'll be with him until the "very end." Buck sums it up: "What does 'the very end' mean here? What does the end of the conflict look like and what is Biden doing to get us there?... This is not the A-Team."

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
